C.	Spreadsheet (Excel) Solutions
----------------------------------
1.	Populate ticket_created_at:
    =XLOOKUP(A2, ticket!E:E, ticket!B:B)
2a. Same day created & closed:
     =COUNTIFS(created_at_range, ">="&A1,
          created_at_range, "<"&A1+1,
          closed_at_range, ">="&A1,
          closed_at_range, "<"&A1+1)

2b. Same hour:
      =COUNTIFS(TEXT(created_at,"yyyy-mm-dd hh"),
             TEXT(closed_at,"yyyy-mm-dd hh"))
